FAST-FORWARD (FF) LIBRARY

FF library contains some useful functionality helping to develop applications in C and C++.

FF is built on top of FFOS which provides cross-platform abilities.  Performance is one of the key aspects of the library: it is designed to run 24/7 in server environment.

FEATURES
	. Base:
		. string
		. array
		. linked-list
		. red-black tree
		. hash table
		. operations with bits

	. Network:
		. URL parser
		. IPv4/IPv6 address convertion functions
		. HTTP
		. DNS
		. SSL (ssleay32)

	. Data:
		. JSON: parse and serialize
		. configuration parser
		. command-line arguments parser
		. deserialization of structured data using a predefined scheme
		. UTF-8 decode/encode

	. Packing/compression:
		. gzip (libz)
		. xz (liblzma)
		. zip (libz)
		. 7z
		. tar

	. Picture:
		. BMP
		. JPEG (libjpeg)
		. PNG (libpng)

	. Audio container:
		.aac (r)
		.flac (w)
		.mp3 (rw)
		.mpc (r)
		.wav (rw)

	. Multimedia container:
		.avi (r)
		.mkv (r)
		.mp4 (rw)
		.ogg (rw)

	. Multimedia meta:
		. APE tag
		. ID3v1
		. ID3v2
		. Vorbis comments

	. Multimedia playlist:
		.cue (r)
		.m3u (rw)
		.pls (r)

	. Audio I/O:
		. Direct Sound playback/capture
		. WASAPI playback/capture
		. ALSA playback/capture
		. Pulse Audio playback
		. OSS playback

	. Audio:
		. ICY
		. PCM operations: mix, convert, gain/attenuate
		. sample rate conversion (libsoxr)
		. APE (libMAC)
		. AAC (libfdk-aac)
		. Vorbis (libvorbis)
		. Opus (libopus)
		. MPEG (libmpg123, libmp3lame)
		. Musepack (libmpc)
		. FLAC (libflac)
		. ALAC (libalac)
		. WavPack (libwavpack)

	. GUI:
		. GUI loader
		. Windows API GUI

	. Database:
		. SQLite (libsqlite)

	. CRC32
	. filesystem path functions
	. user task queue
	. timer queue
	. file mapping

